<br />\n我google左 多數人都係去到先搵當地教練教<br />\n10000円全日<br />\n不過1月頭怕好多人<br />\n有無巴打有無得book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係響官網有條link可以book定？<br />\n如果去到搵唔到人教俾人屌到開花都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，大把人咩都唔識係度玩<br />\n最緊要留番度係新手滑道就ok<br />\n利申：上年唔識滑走去gala玩"},{"pid":"a73635af9a6eae208691790cbcced3cf46500d7c","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟1月頭打算去GALA滑雪場<br />\n初次滑雪想有個教練教下咁<br />\n我google左 多數人都係去到先搵當地教練教<br />\n10000円全日<br />\n不過1月頭怕好多人<br />\n有無巴打有無得book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係響官網有條link可以book定？<br />\n如果去到搵唔到人教俾人屌到開花都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，大把人咩都唔識係度玩<br />\n最緊要留番度係新手滑道就ok<br />\n利申：上年唔識滑走去gala玩</blockquote><br />\n官網個個係有間叫Canyon既教滑雪 5000円1.5hrs<br />\n不過我上網見好多人都有話10000円包埋租雪具一天同車卷 不過我見親既都係walkin<br />\n想知道有無得book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee6d667f952c37ea21df71666e1a531bb86aa28","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我一月都定左去越後湯沢同GALA玩下雪🤩都想知會唔會好多人要book</blockquote><br />\n我都怕一月好多人 見trip advisor有人話去到無哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a840b03190970dc11e35fd494f2564abb07d0f23","tid":466143,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我一月都定左去越後湯沢同GALA玩下雪🤩都想知會唔會好多人要book</blockquote><br />\n我都怕一月好多人 見trip advisor有人話去到無哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕多人就唔好去gala,要排隊咁滑雪"},{"pid":"601ffb1ef6e867314b08dbf22a1bb4d3060f2b7e","tid":466143,"uid":56206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:34:04.000Z","msg":"東京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4209ee75cde96aa6728243c25a5dc1dedf6560d3","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我一月都定左去越後湯沢同GALA玩下雪🤩都想知會唔會好多人要book</blockquote><br />\n我都怕一月好多人 見trip advisor有人話去到無哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕多人就唔好去gala,要排隊咁滑雪</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無邊到推薦 有諗過輕井澤不過啲雪好似係人工  滑得就想滑下真雪 所以揀GALA"},{"pid":"8e7795d2f72c65e8bc15453de460a8c9fd74fdee","tid":466143,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T13:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟1月頭打算去GALA滑雪場<br />\n初次滑雪想有個教練教下咁<br />\n我google左 多數人都係去到先搵當地教練教<br />\n10000円全日<br />\n不過1月頭怕好多人<br />\n有無巴打有無得book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係響官網有條link可以book定？<br />\n如果去到搵唔到人教俾人屌到開花都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，大把人咩都唔識係度玩<br />\n最緊要留番度係新手滑道就ok<br />\n利申：上年唔識滑走去gala玩</blockquote><br />\n官網個個係有間叫Canyon既教滑雪 5000円1.5hrs<br />\n不過我上網見好多人都有話10000円包埋租雪具一天同車卷 不過我見親既都係walkin<br />\n想知道有無得book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我理解係show JR pass 可以有優惠，大約 10000円=租雪具+服裝+車卷，但未計學費喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/R5WRvh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FR5WRvh&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=87fb8c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/R5WRvh</a><br />\n<br />\nCanyon 講明係除咗有個教練，乜撚都唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>What is not included?<br />\n<br />\nYou will need to arrange your own ski or snowboard equipment and lift tickets. It is important to wear waterproof clothing, a hat or helmet, gloves and goggles. All equipment can be rented when you arrive at GALA resort. Please arrive at least 1.5 hours before your lesson to arrange rental, purchase lift tickets and get changed.</em>"},{"pid":"0506d1c30e67d5e401259660745c877414793838","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-12T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟1月頭打算去GALA滑雪場<br />\n初次滑雪想有個教練教下咁<br />\n我google左 多數人都係去到先搵當地教練教<br />\n10000円全日<br />\n不過1月頭怕好多人<br />\n有無巴打有無得book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係響官網有條link可以book定？<br />\n如果去到搵唔到人教俾人屌到開花都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，大把人咩都唔識係度玩<br />\n最緊要留番度係新手滑道就ok<br />\n利申：上年唔識滑走去gala玩</blockquote><br />\n官網個個係有間叫Canyon既教滑雪 5000円1.5hrs<br />\n不過我上網見好多人都有話10000円包埋租雪具一天同車卷 不過我見親既都係walkin<br />\n想知道有無得book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我理解係show JR pass 可以有優惠，大約 10000円=租雪具+服裝+車卷，但未計學費喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/R5WRvh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FR5WRvh&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=87fb8c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/R5WRvh</a><br />\n<br />\nCanyon 講明係除咗有個教練，乜撚都唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>What is not included?<br />\n<br />\nYou will need to arrange your own ski or snowboard equipment and lift tickets. It is important to wear waterproof clothing, a hat or helmet, gloves and goggles. All equipment can be rented when you arrive at GALA resort. Please arrive at least 1.5 hours before your lesson to arrange rental, purchase lift tickets and get changed.</em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cardu.com.tw/detail.php?T=B&amp;K=14217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cardu.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3FT%3DB%26K%3D14217&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3e09445e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cardu.com.tw/detail.php?T=B&amp;K=14217</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/004912_0e1df617b4370293fd83fde66e736ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F004912_0e1df617b4370293fd83fde66e736ae4.jpg&h=60010b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網睇好似話個到都有依種套票買 <br />\nCanyon 5000円 只有教學 但係有得book<br />\n滑雪場個個就10000円全包咁濟 但係我見親都係walkin"},{"pid":"ebdd0c91fb14c22023db8fb3c9b601696738af78","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T01:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4a1bb13709bac0916c93febb3233d01a4dac6d","tid":466143,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我一月都定左去越後湯沢同GALA玩下雪🤩都想知會唔會好多人要book</blockquote><br />\n我都怕一月好多人 見trip advisor有人話去到無哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕多人就唔好去gala,要排隊咁滑雪</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無邊到推薦 有諗過輕井澤不過啲雪好似係人工  滑得就想滑下真雪 所以揀GALA</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係絲<br />\ngala因為係jR子公司同交通方便所以先咁出名多遊客去，1月去除左好南果D場，差不多全日本都有真雪滑，btw你係味一定搭jr先?"},{"pid":"32e2c45af17132341be46bc6e7b9b0641c8a073f","tid":466143,"uid":60480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟1月頭打算去GALA滑雪場<br />\n初次滑雪想有個教練教下咁<br />\n我google左 多數人都係去到先搵當地教練教<br />\n10000円全日<br />\n不過1月頭怕好多人<br />\n有無巴打有無得book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係響官網有條link可以book定？<br />\n如果去到搵唔到人教俾人屌到開花都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，大把人咩都唔識係度玩<br />\n最緊要留番度係新手滑道就ok<br />\n利申：上年唔識滑走去gala玩</blockquote><br />\n官網個個係有間叫Canyon既教滑雪 5000円1.5hrs<br />\n不過我上網見好多人都有話10000円包埋租雪具一天同車卷 不過我見親既都係walkin<br />\n想知道有無得book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我理解係show JR pass 可以有優惠，大約 10000円=租雪具+服裝+車卷，但未計學費喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/R5WRvh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FR5WRvh&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=87fb8c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/R5WRvh</a><br />\n<br />\nCanyon 講明係除咗有個教練，乜撚都唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>What is not included?<br />\n<br />\nYou will need to arrange your own ski or snowboard equipment and lift tickets. It is important to wear waterproof clothing, a hat or helmet, gloves and goggles. All equipment can be rented when you arrive at GALA resort. Please arrive at least 1.5 hours before your lesson to arrange rental, purchase lift tickets and get changed.</em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cardu.com.tw/detail.php?T=B&amp;K=14217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cardu.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3FT%3DB%26K%3D14217&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3e09445e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cardu.com.tw/detail.php?T=B&amp;K=14217</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/004912_0e1df617b4370293fd83fde66e736ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F004912_0e1df617b4370293fd83fde66e736ae4.jpg&h=60010b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網睇好似話個到都有依種套票買 <br />\nCanyon 5000円 只有教學 但係有得book<br />\n滑雪場個個就10000円全包咁濟 但係我見親都係walkin</blockquote><br />\n我睇youtube都見到你呢個優惠,不過係今年一月,唔知新一年有冇唔同"},{"pid":"0d17fa3afc4025ffbfb249a57da5a44b0f9ef67f","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:17:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我一月都定左去越後湯沢同GALA玩下雪🤩都想知會唔會好多人要book</blockquote><br />\n我都怕一月好多人 見trip advisor有人話去到無哂位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n怕多人就唔好去gala,要排隊咁滑雪</blockquote><br />\n巴打有無邊到推薦 有諗過輕井澤不過啲雪好似係人工  滑得就想滑下真雪 所以揀GALA</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我係絲<br />\ngala因為係jR子公司同交通方便所以先咁出名多遊客去，1月去除左好南果D場，差不多全日本都有真雪滑，btw你係味一定搭jr先?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n河絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唔一定JR 其實只要方便就得 因為想朝早就開始 東京去既話唔想花太多時間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真雪 方便 有教練 依三樣都有就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d31196edf0dbe33d4ddd4f371da57b3b8bf4745","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:19:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>小弟1月頭打算去GALA滑雪場<br />\n初次滑雪想有個教練教下咁<br />\n我google左 多數人都係去到先搵當地教練教<br />\n10000円全日<br />\n不過1月頭怕好多人<br />\n有無巴打有無得book定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係響官網有條link可以book定？<br />\n如果去到搵唔到人教俾人屌到開花都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會，大把人咩都唔識係度玩<br />\n最緊要留番度係新手滑道就ok<br />\n利申：上年唔識滑走去gala玩</blockquote><br />\n官網個個係有間叫Canyon既教滑雪 5000円1.5hrs<br />\n不過我上網見好多人都有話10000円包埋租雪具一天同車卷 不過我見親既都係walkin<br />\n想知道有無得book<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我理解係show JR pass 可以有優惠，大約 10000円=租雪具+服裝+車卷，但未計學費喎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/R5WRvh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FR5WRvh&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=87fb8c1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/R5WRvh</a><br />\n<br />\nCanyon 講明係除咗有個教練，乜撚都唔包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<em>What is not included?<br />\n<br />\nYou will need to arrange your own ski or snowboard equipment and lift tickets. It is important to wear waterproof clothing, a hat or helmet, gloves and goggles. All equipment can be rented when you arrive at GALA resort. Please arrive at least 1.5 hours before your lesson to arrange rental, purchase lift tickets and get changed.</em></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.cardu.com.tw/detail.php?T=B&amp;K=14217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.cardu.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3FT%3DB%26K%3D14217&d=GDco4eikgCNzwlCeCv518pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=3e09445e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.cardu.com.tw/detail.php?T=B&amp;K=14217</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/004912_0e1df617b4370293fd83fde66e736ae4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F004912_0e1df617b4370293fd83fde66e736ae4.jpg&h=60010b48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我上網睇好似話個到都有依種套票買 <br />\nCanyon 5000円 只有教學 但係有得book<br />\n滑雪場個個就10000円全包咁濟 但係我見親都係walkin</blockquote><br />\n我睇youtube都見到你呢個優惠,不過係今年一月,唔知新一年有冇唔同</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宜家先十一月 未見有人報告返黎 佢個官網資料又唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唯有靠上年資料睇"},{"pid":"3c02eac61c647132d61e968ff1f53d0b774ba644","tid":466143,"uid":18743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8401a00467edb62dfa4e0a78cce693049f31676","tid":466143,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:52:24.000Z","msg":"Gala可以滑過去石打丸山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885e6229e658e138c8b9216c730efb6175dd38d9","tid":466143,"uid":1080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T10:55:58.000Z","msg":"我12月尾會去 之前學過一次 都諗緊洗唔洗去到再搵人教"},{"pid":"121caacaaf5c07878b3ad391c0d718124c5ea0ff","tid":466143,"uid":18743,