><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢個場都幾方便<br />\n個陣膽粗粗唔識滑租左單板去玩<br />\n玩到最後覺得人一世物一世乜都試下 上埋啲高手場<br />\n係咁仆街都覺得好好玩好開心<br />\n不過第二朝好似比人打左全身咁好酸痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ski 會唔會咁<br />\n仲諗住第一日上堂，第二日自己玩</blockquote><br />\n我都係諗住去兩日 睇下第一日可唔可以搵到教練 <br />\n搵唔到就自己練返熟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你可以試下去跑10km睇下第二日會唔會成身酸痛<br />\n滑雪仲要用埋你平時用唔到的肌肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有乜位置嘅肌肉值得操咗先，唔洗搞到成身酸痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：跑開步加有練少少手臂</blockquote><br />\n我覺得係大脾同小腿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我第一次去玩板，的確係腳用力多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跑步都係跑，但玩板要用腳拉成個人起身<br />\n滑完一次已經無哂力"},{"pid":"2908642819a4e88af5ab7b37333d6502afb19b42","tid":466143,"uid":108592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一月中想去東京滑一日<br />\n但同行者唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有冇人會去 想搵個伴<br />\n<br />\n新手</blockquote><br />\n我都係一月中想去玩一日 第一次滑 你幾號去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4622348b537a32036a844bc97a32af8d6ebf980d","tid":466143,"uid":51879,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T14:08:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一月中想去東京滑一日<br />\n但同行者唔想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知有冇人會去 想搵個伴<br />\n<br />\n新手</blockquote><br />\n我都係一月中想去玩一日 第一次滑 你幾號去?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n18-22"},{"pid":"b471bdb6f416ffc1224ce0b608b45267263cf335","tid":466143,"uid":154174,"lik